---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | Newcastle Table Tennis"
  description="Newcastle Table Tennis Club has been operating since 1996. We are a volunteer-run, non-profit club affiliated with PCYC and Table Tennis NSW."
>
  <div class="bg-neutral-50 py-16 min-h-screen">
      
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-6">About Our Club</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        Bringing table tennis to the Hunter region since 1996.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-200 p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-neutral-600">
            <p class="mb-6">
                Newcastle PCYC Table Tennis Club has been a fixture of the local sporting community for nearly 30 years. What started as a small group of enthusiasts has grown into one of the most active table tennis clubs in regional NSW.
            </p>
            <p>
                Based at the PCYC in Broadmeadow, we provide a professional yet welcoming environment for everyoneâ€”from casual social players to state-ranked competitors. We are entirely volunteer-run, driven by a passion for the sport and a commitment to our members.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Our Values</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 mt-0.5">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="ml-3 text-neutral-700"><strong>Inclusive:</strong> We welcome players of all ages, backgrounds, and abilities.</span>
                </li>
                 <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 mt-0.5">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="ml-3 text-neutral-700"><strong>Community:</strong> We foster a friendly, social atmosphere where respect is paramount.</span>
                </li>
                 <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 mt-0.5">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="ml-3 text-neutral-700"><strong>Affordable:</strong> We keep fees low to ensure the sport remains accessible.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Affiliations</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-500 font-bold text-xs">PCYC</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-neutral-900">PCYC Newcastle</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Venue Partner</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-500 font-bold text-xs">TTNSW</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-neutral-900">Table Tennis NSW</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Affiliated Club</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-primary-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Come meet the team</h2>
        <p class="text-primary-200 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            The best way to get to know us is to come down for a hit. Your first session is completely free.
        </p>
        <a href="/timetable" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-primary-900 bg-white hover:bg-neutral-50 transition shadow-lg">
            See Session Times
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
